The basic idea is that we first perform DFS from one of the island (any cell of first island ), and when we perform DFS we mark them as visited and also we pus these cells in the queue. And as soon as we successfully perform DFS from 1st island we break and start performing BFS. The advantage we get is that all the cells of 1st island is marked as visited but the cells of 2nd island is still unvisited, **so we can distinguish between them using visited matrix.** Now when we perfrom BFS we try to reach the cells of 2nd island which is identifined as grid value as 1 and unvisted. This way BFS give shortest path as it is a shortest path algo.

