# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
I thought we can run make a visited 2D array and make it true for either island and then run multisource bfs until we reach the second island. 
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
1. Make a 2d Visited array and make it true for either island.
2. Run MultiSource BFS until you reach second island.
# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
O(N^2)
- Space complexity:
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
O(N^2) N is size of graph
